\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 What this model does\

\f1\b0 This model simulates a 4-stage beer supply chain:\
Retailer -> Wholesaler -> Distributor -> Factory\
The goal is to keep the whole supply chain cost as low as possible each week by balancing:\
\
Inventory cost: $0.25 per unit per week\
Backlog cost: $1.00 per unit per week\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 ------------------------------------------------\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Weekly flow (what happens every week)\

\f1\b0 Each week, the model runs this sequence:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Each role receives any shipments arriving this week.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Each role receives incoming demand/orders:\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Retailer gets customer demand directly.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Other roles get delayed orders from downstream.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Each role ships as much as possible using on-hand inventory to satisfy:\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}backlog + new incoming order\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Unmet demand becomes backlog.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Weekly costs are calculated:\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}InvCost = inventory \'d7 0.25\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}BackCost = backlog \'d7 1.00\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Each role places a new order upstream (Factory places a production order).\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \

\f0\b Delays (key concept)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Order information delay: 2 weeks\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Shipping/production delay: 2 weeks\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Total time from placing an order to receiving goods: about 4 weeks\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
