\f0\b \cf0 How the optimizer works (simple)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}    Tries many candidate base-stock policies\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}    Simulates each policy forward from the current state\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}    Selects the policy with the lowest total cost\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}    Converts that policy into this week\'92s recommended orders\
